Bills End 15-Game Losing Streak Versus Patriots to Stay Unbeaten

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-09-25T20:37:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/bills-end-15-game-losing-streak-versus-patriots-to-stay-unbeaten.html
The  Buffalo Bills  beat the  New
England Patriots  to end a 15-game losing streak against their
division rival in the  National Football League .  Rian Lindell kicked a 28-yard field goal with three seconds
remaining to seal a 34-31 comeback win for the Bills at Ralph
Wilson Stadium in Buffalo,  New York .  Buffalo improves to 3-0 after handing  New England  its first
defeat of the season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  